      "updated": 1782889700188,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Reflects D-025 Departments (task-level access), D-027 publish gate, D-029 collab doc delete, D-030 single-tier MVP (no custom domain / no white-label / Powered-by-Siapp always shown), D-032 no per-task Requires-photo / Requires-approval, D-033 timeline-only project board, D-034 client portal upload + start date + timespan bar. Due dates optional. Client portal is READ + client-upload for shared documents.",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 5,
