      "type": "text",
      "x": 40,
      "y": 9272,
      "width": 1200,
      "height": 16,
      "text": "Per D-031: no customer-facing project templates in MVP. Two-mode chooser - Blank or Duplicate from an existing project. The starter project itself is seeded by Siapp Admin during tenant provisioning ([Z2]).",
      "fontSize": 11,
