      "x": 258,
      "y": 15664,
      "width": 1044,
      "height": 16,
      "text": "Approval state syncs from Twilio Content Templates API every 5 min. Submit new revision opens a form that posts to Twilio + writes to auditLog. Customers see only the active Approved version on [A9].",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
